{"type": "article", "id": 30748, "title": "GAP 还在跌，以及，innisfree 推出 DIY 气垫粉底 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-09T02:27:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1901, "name": "MiuMiu"}, {"id": 5498, "name": "Cartier"}, {"id": 12406, "name": "Innisfree"}, {"id": 21375, "name": "The Horse"}, {"id": 321, "name": "Amazon"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 31242, "name": "Fullbeauty"}, {"id": 31243, "name": "Galvan"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808204852vfokPwMbe8p0xn7N.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/galvan-launches-e-commerce-plans-for-bridal-10502578/\" rel=\"nofollow\">英国礼服品牌 Galvan 开始了电商业务 </a></b>| 成立两年，以怀旧优雅著称的的英国礼服品牌 Galvan 在这周开始了它的电商业务，并且宣称，将在 2017 年，开拓婚纱市场。<br></p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/amazon-fashion-launches-in-mexico-despite-major-challenges-10502471/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Amazon 开辟墨西哥市场 </a></b>| 此前，Amazon 已经售卖了超过五千万件商品。这次给墨西哥市场带来了 Calvin Klein, Lee , Steve Madden 和 Desigual 这些品牌。</p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/fullbeauty-brands-launches-ellos-as-plus-size-brand-for-online-and-catalogue-10502410/\" rel=\"nofollow\">大码服饰集团 Fullbeauty 入驻瑞典时尚电商 Ellos</a></b> | Fullbeauty 于 2012 年年底被开云集团抛售，在 2015 年被全球性的私募基金公司 Apax Parterns 收购。此次入驻瑞典领先的时尚电商 Ellos，并计划于 8 月 22 日合作推出北欧风格的大码服装。&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/gap-comp-sales-july-10503316/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>GAP 第二季度销售额进一步下滑</b></a> | GAP 发布第二季度财报显示，该集团的第二季度净利润为 11 亿美元，低于去年同期的 11.2 亿美元，下降了约 2%，大大超过了之前的分析师预测 （下跌 0.3%）。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Coach-results-to-underscore-turnaround-success,721330.html#.V6ka9GXcyT8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Coach 第二季度表现良好</b></a> | 由于 Coach 进行品牌的重新定位，削减了促销活动和减少在百货公司的库存，以远离低价促销。这些措施帮助它在第二季度，北美同店销售增长了 1.8 ％。今年以来，Coach 的股价已经上涨了 28%。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">Cartier 发布全新 Magicien 高级珠宝系列，由钻石、蓝宝石、红碧玺、祖母绿等珍贵宝石打造而成。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204309e1Gj8VwSfBN57nbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082043192OW0uZom6qxBYMfc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204329hiAdX5IgVsJYMfea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204337T82zfRPCQuIhZ1E7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">韩国人气美妆品牌 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/innisfree-100-hk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">innisfree 的 DIY 气垫粉底</a>正式登陆香港，共有 100 多款粉底盒可以自行搭配。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204409Shel7Z52JHRfq0F6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204418iOQXg3tIeWw4H9GE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082044277BqaDHnlRbxoswGT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Gucci 更新了部分 2016 秋冬季新品，延续了之前的复古浪漫的风格。 这一次的 GucciSylvie 包使用了黑色的 Gucci 经典皮革。而新的 Gucci 拖鞋，则采用了玫瑰刺绣。 酒神包推出了新的款式，并有黑白两色可以选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808223942zxLm23tWXFwZbcs5.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770355\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808223954HDVZYsThcC68qSv2.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.782427\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082240158ruqSZsKze6l4U9T.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779412\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082240423BpuPeqIymCAKgVs.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.782427\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>来自澳洲的小清新手表品牌 the horse ，最近推出了几款包包，延续了一贯的清新质感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080820452545fJuRXmleEgd619.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204533vzJoSG6Q0jOr9Zs7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204541EuItCxqP2kTsAypO.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.994992\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>miumiu 的 2016 秋冬季新品发布，关键词：牛仔、纽扣、长筒袜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204638TtdCpScaXLw9AMDB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.240166\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082046315uMVx4QsTjF7gO6C.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250522\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204624PlmtgsfdyWuc5JeA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.069272\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204618Sozws8F0Y69uUjOR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001678\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204550w75XymisZHu0UevM.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204558qypOcZzCGioxVwjX.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.008446\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}